for nbc and produce other documentaries for pbs as well as the 
national geographic series 
the principal writer of the film is journalist sanford ungar 
dean of the school of communications at american university in 
washington dc whose father was born in czechoslovakia 
the documentary is a pilot for a possible new series on eastern 
bloc countries 
