<TEXT>
a lack of preparation also showed in the shoddy construction of 
apartment houses that crumbled on their residents and worsened the 
tragedy even though leninakan spitak and other northwestern 
armenian cities are in an earthquake zone the same kinds of 
prefabricated apartments were built there as in other parts of the 
