rough is accused of disclosing information on the discount rate 
set by the federal reserve bank in washington to principals at 
bevill bresler amp schulman inc a brokerage firm based in 
livingston nj that later suffered a 144 million collapse 
the government said bevill bresler made millions of dollars and 
